<!-- STOP: including template: extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/templates/partials/body/page_actions.tpl (extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/templates/partials/body/page_actions.tpl) -->
    <!--Content-Begin-->
    <article>
            <h1>Sikre trampoliner til privat brug</h1>
      <summary>
        <p>
                      
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/eztext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/eztext.tpl) -->

Trampoliner til privat brug er legetøj og skal overholde reglerne om legetøjssikkerhed. Der må således ikke være nogen uacceptabel fare for sikkerheden, hvis trampolinen bruges, som man må forvente, at børn vil anvende den. 
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/eztext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/eztext.tpl) -->
                            </p>
      </summary>
      <div class="pull-right social-icons">
<!-- START: including template: extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/templates/partials/body/social_icons.tpl (extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/templates/partials/body/social_icons.tpl) -->
<a href="https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https://sik.dk/Virksomhed/Produktsikkerhed-for-fagfolk/Vejledninger-om-produktsikkerhed/Sikre-trampoliner-til-privat-brug" target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-facebook-square facebook-brand"></i></a>
<a href="http://twitter.com/share?url=https://sik.dk/Virksomhed/Produktsikkerhed-for-fagfolk/Vejledninger-om-produktsikkerhed/Sikre-trampoliner-til-privat-brug" target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-twitter-square twitter-brand"></i></a>
<a href="https://pinterest.com/pin/create/button/?url=https://sik.dk/Virksomhed/Produktsikkerhed-for-fagfolk/Vejledninger-om-produktsikkerhed/Sikre-trampoliner-til-privat-brug" target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-pinterest-square pinterest-brand"></i></a>
<a href="https://www.linkedin.com/shareArticle?mini=true&amp;url=https://sik.dk/Virksomhed/Produktsikkerhed-for-fagfolk/Vejledninger-om-produktsikkerhed/Sikre-trampoliner-til-privat-brug" target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-linkedin-square linkedin-brand"></i></a>
<a href="mailto:?subject=Sikre trampoliner til privat brug&body=https://sik.dk/Virksomhed/Produktsikkerhed-for-fagfolk/Vejledninger-om-produktsikkerhed/Sikre-trampoliner-til-privat-brug" target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-envelope-o mail-brand"></i></a>

<!-- STOP: including template: extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/templates/partials/body/social_icons.tpl (extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/templates/partials/body/social_icons.tpl) -->
</div>
      <br>
      <hr>
                  <div class="content-image pull-right">
            <img src="../../../var/plain_site/storage/images/forside/virksomhed/produktsi/Sikre-trampoliner-til-p" class="img-responsive" alt="" />
            
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl) -->


<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl) -->
          </div>
        
              
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl) -->


<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Dansk Standard har udgivet den første europæiske standard for trampoliner til privat brug, EN 71-14, den 14. januar 2015.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Standarden er offentliggjort i EU-Tidende 13. marts 2015. Dermed er standarden harmoniseret og giver fabrikanten ret til at formode, at hans trampolin overholder de gældende sikkerhedskrav for legetøj.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
<b>Typegodkendelse eller standard</b>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>En fabrikant kan vælge, om han vil følge standarden eller have sit produkt typegodkendt, før det lovligt kan sælges til privat brug på det danske marked.. Tidligere har der været krav om, at trampoliner skulle typegodkendes. &nbsp;</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Standarden indeholder en lang række anbefalinger omkring materialevalg, opbygning af trampolinen og information til brugerne om anvendelsen. &nbsp;Blandt andet nævnes det for trampoliner over 150 centimeter i diameter, at de skal være forsynet med sikkerhedsnet og at åbningen i nettet skal have en vis højde og kunne åbnes indefra.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
<b>Standard gælder ikke nedgravede trampoliner</b>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Standarden omfatter kun trampoliner, der står oven på jorden. For nedgravede trampoliner skal der fortsat gives en typegodkendelse. Det forventes, at standarden hurtigt vil blive revideret, så den også dækker nedgravede trampoliner. En revideret udgave af standarden kan dog først ventes at være på plads i 2018.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>For nedgravede trampoliner vil en række forhold være anderledes end for fritstående trampoliner. Ved sikkerhedsvurderingen bør fabrikanten derfor som minimum overveje:</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/ul.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/ul.tpl) -->

<ul>

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl) -->

<li>Er der behov for sikkerhedsnet?</li>

<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl) -->

<li>Er der risiko for at falde ned mellem trampolin og udgravningens kant?</li>

<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl) -->

<li>Er der risiko for, at dugen under brug vil ramme bunden af udgravningen?</li>

<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl) -->

<li>Er der risiko for at overse et barn eller et dyr, som gemmer sig under dugen?</li>

<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl) -->

<li>Er der risiko for øget korrosion af stellet?</li>

<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl) -->

</ul>

<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/ul.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/ul.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
<b>Hovedindholdet i den kommende standard</b>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Standarden definerer tre typer trampoliner til forskellige målgrupper, hvor vilkårene omkring trampolinens udformning og udstyr varierer lidt.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/ul.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/ul.tpl) -->

<ul>

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl) -->

<li>En minitrampolin har en ramme på under 150 cm i diameter og er mindre end 35 centimeter høj. Minitrampolinen er beregnet til brugere, som højst vejer 25 kg. Minitrampolinen kan være forsynet med rækværk til støtte for brugeren eller med sikkerhedsnet.</li>

<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl) -->

<li>En mellemstørrelse trampolin måler mellem 150 og 250 centimeter, er mindst 35 centimeter høj og er beregnet til brugere på højst 50 kg. Den skal udstyres med sikkerhedsnet.</li>

<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl) -->

<li>En stor trampolin måler over 250 centimeter og har en ramme på mindst 35 centimeters højde. Brugerens maksimumvægt på en stor trampolin fastlægges af fabrikanten. Trampolinen skal have sikkerhedsnet.</li>

<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl) -->

</ul>

<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/ul.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/ul.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
<b>Standardens krav</b>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Hvis fabrikanten vælger at følge standarden, skal han sælge sikkerhedsnettet sammen med trampolinen. Når man køber et separat sikkerhedsnet, skal der være klar information om, hvilke trampoliner nettet passer til.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Fabrikanten vil skulle sikre, at trampolinen er tydeligt mærket med, at den kun må bruges af én person ad gangen. Kravene om sikkerhedsnet og om kun at hoppe en ad gangen skal imødegå de to største risici for ulykker - fald fra trampolinen og sammenstød.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Den frivillige standard definerer ikke, hvilke materialer en trampolin skal opbygges af, men der vil være krav til brudstyrke for trampolindug og kantpuder og til metaldelene på trampolinen.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Ved konstruktionen skal det sikres, at det ikke er muligt at få hoved, fingre eller fødder i klemme i eller mellem de dele, der indgår i trampolinen. Det er fastlagt, hvor store åbninger der for eksempel må være i en trampolindug eller mellem fjedre.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Der er ligeledes anvisninger på, hvordan kantpuder skal udformes og hvordan stænger skal beskyttes.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Derudover indgår det i den frivillige standard, hvordan advarselsmærkningen på trampolinen skal udformes. Det understreges blandt andet, at der skal være en synlig markering på trampolinen af maksimumvægten for brugerne og at det er vigtigt at lukke sikkerhedsnettet før brugen.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Desuden giver standarden en oversigt over, hvad der skal indgå i vejledningen til forbrugerne, for eksempel at trampolinen bør placeres på et jævnt underlag og med mindst to meters afstand fra hegn, bygninger, tørresnore og elledninger.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
<b>Når du fremstiller trampoliner</b>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Det er fabrikantens ansvar, at en trampolin overholder sikkerhedskravene i legetøjsbekendtgørelsen. Dertil kommer mere konkrete krav i enten standarden eller typegodkendelsen, hvor der blandt andet vil være specificeret en række krav om information til dem, der køber produktet.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Da der i Danmark har været en udbredt brug af overjordiske trampoliner til nedgravning i private haver, bør fabrikantens information tage højde for, at denne særlige anvendelse er forudsigelig brug.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
<b>Når du sælger trampoliner</b>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Distributøren skal sikre sig, at lovpligtig mærkning og de krævede oplysninger i salgssituationen er til stede. Informationen skal være på dansk.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Distributøren har et medansvar for, at der kun sælges sikre trampoliner. Hvis han har kendskab til, at der er eller kan være et sikkerhedsproblem ved legetøjet, skal han handle med fornøden omhu.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Distributøren skal sikre sig, at forbrugerne får den nødvendige sikkerhedsinformation på dansk om opsætning, brug og vedligeholdelse af trampolinen, herunder information om, hvorvidt trampolinen er egnet til nedgravning.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
<b>Læs mere</b>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Standarder kan købes hos 
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/link.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/link.tpl) -->
<a href="https://webshop.ds.dk/da-dk/forside" title="Link til Dansk Standard Webshop" target="_blank">Dansk Standard Webshop</a>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/link.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/link.tpl) -->
</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/InfoBox.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/InfoBox.tpl) -->
<div class="alert alert-info">
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
<b>Flere typer trampoliner</b>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Trampoliner til privat brug er legetøj og skal opfylde kravene til legetøjssikkerhed. Det betyder, at der ikke må være en uacceptabel sikkerhedsrisiko, når trampolinen anvendes, som den er konstrueret til, eller som man må forvente, at børn vil gøre.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Gymnastiktrampoliner og trampoliner på legepladser og i boligforeninger er ikke omfattet af legetøjsreglerne.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Af hensyn til sikkerheden er det altid vigtigt at følge fabrikantens anvisninger omkring anvendelse og vedligeholdelse.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
</div>

<!-- STOP: including template: extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/InfoBox.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/InfoBox.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/InfoBox.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/InfoBox.tpl) -->
<div class="alert alert-info">
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
<b>Risiko for ulykker</b>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Størstedelen af ulykkerne på private trampoliner er faldulykker, viser ulykkesstatistik fra Odense Universitetshospital.&nbsp; Der sker flest ulykker ved fald i vandret niveau, men der er også mange fald fra højden. Desuden sker der et stort antal forvridninger, og der sker sammenstød mellem flere personer.&nbsp; I statistikken registreres der kun få ulykker som følge af vindforhold, materialefejl eller fejlfunktion af trampolinen.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
</div>

<!-- STOP: including template: extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/InfoBox.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/InfoBox.tpl) -->

<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl) -->
      
      
